        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Account/Register">Sign Up! &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Create Recipes</h2>
        <p>Use the recipe builder to add ingredients and methodologies to your recipe. </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Dashboard">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
